languages.text: {n}Осклабившись, воин запускает пятерню в грязные волосы, придавая себе еще более дикий вид.{/n} "Тебе зачем то знать, а?"
{n}Grinning, the warrior runs his fingers through his dirty hair, making himself look even wilder in the process.{/n} "And why do you want to know?"
languages.original_text: {n}Осклабившись, воин запускает пятерню в грязные волосы, придавая себе еще более дикий вид.{/n} "Тебе зачем то знать, а?"

traits.locale_text: {n}Grinning stupidly, the warrior runs his fingers through his dirty hair, making himself look even wilder in the process.{/n} "Escape? What for? Here I eat, here I kill. Why would I want to leave?"
traits.speaker: UlfarInPrison

languages.text: {n}这位战士露出了笑容，用手指捋了捋肮脏的头发。他的表情看起来更加粗野。{/n}“你问这些话，是出于什么目的？”
languages.original_text: {n}Grinning, the warrior runs his fingers through his dirty hair, making himself look even wilder in the process.{/n} "And why do you want to know?"

traits.locale_text: {n}这位战士露出了呆滞的笑容，用手指捋了捋肮脏的头发。他的表情看起来更加粗野。{/n}“逃跑？我干吗要逃跑？我在这里有饭吃，又有人杀，我为什么要逃跑？”
traits.speaker: UlfarInPrison

languages.text: {n}戦士は愚鈍そうに笑い、汚れた髪を手でかきあげながらより一層野性味のある風貌で答えた。{/n}「なぜ、そんなことが知りたい？」
languages.original_text: {n}Grinning, the warrior runs his fingers through his dirty hair, making himself look even wilder in the process.{/n} "And why do you want to know?"

traits.locale_text: {n}戦士は愚鈍そうに笑い、汚れた髪を手でかきあげながらより一層野性味のある風貌で答えた。{/n}「脱出？何のために？ここにいりゃ食事にありつけるし、殺せる。楽園のような場所じゃないか」
traits.speaker: UlfarInPrison

languages.text: {n}Sonriendo, el guerrero se pasa la mano por la sucia melena, quedando aún más desaliñado.{/n} «¿Y a usted qué le importa?».
languages.original_text: {n}Grinning, the warrior runs his fingers through his dirty hair, making himself look even wilder in the process.{/n} "And why do you want to know?"

traits.locale_text: {n}Sonriendo como un bobo, el guerrero se pasa la mano por la sucia melena, quedando aún más desaliñado.{/n} «¿Escapar? ¿Para qué? Aquí puedo comer y matar. ¿Para qué iba a querer marcharme?».
traits.speaker: UlfarInPrison

languages.text: {n}Un sourire aux lèvres, le guerrier passe ses doigts dans ses cheveux sales et parvient vous ne savez comment à les rendre encore plus hirsutes.{/n} « Qu'est-ce que ça peut vous faire ? »
languages.original_text: {n}Grinning, the warrior runs his fingers through his dirty hair, making himself look even wilder in the process.{/n} "And why do you want to know?"

traits.locale_text: {n}Avec un sourire béat, le guerrier passe ses doigts dans ses cheveux sales et parvient vous ne savez comment à les rendre encore plus hirsutes.{/n} « M'évader ? Pour quoi faire ? Ici, je mange et je tue. Pourquoi est-ce que je voudrais partir ? »
traits.speaker: UlfarInPrison

languages.text: {n}Grinsend fährt sich der Krieger mit den Fingern durch sein schmutziges Haar und sieht danach noch wilder aus.{/n} "Und warum wollt Ihr das wissen?"
languages.original_text: {n}Grinning, the warrior runs his fingers through his dirty hair, making himself look even wilder in the process.{/n} "And why do you want to know?"

traits.locale_text: {n}Mit dummem Grinsen fährt der Krieger sich mit den Fingern durch sein schmutziges Haar und sieht danach noch wilder aus.{/n} "Flucht? Warum denn? Ich esse hier, ich töte hier. Weshalb sollte ich wegwollen?"
traits.speaker: UlfarInPrison
